        <div class="future-section__preview">
          <div class="future-section__preview-title text-font font-title">
            Coffee
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="future-section__content future-coffee">
          <h2 class="future-coffee__title font-title">
            <div class="future-coffee__title-top">Coffee</div>
            <div class="future-coffee__title-sub">KOPPE 4th Wave Project</div>
          </h2>
          <div class="future-coffee__about">
            <Image
              src={FutureCoffeeAboutImg}
              width={323}
              height={535}
              alt="KOPPE 4th Wave Project"
              class:list={"future-coffee__about-img"}
            />
            <div class="future-coffee__about-descr">
              <b class="future-coffee__about-descr-title">
                Style <br /> Creates Culture
              </b>
              <p class="future-coffee__about-descr-text font-text-content">
                KOPPE is dedicated to creating a new coffee culture known as the
                “4th Wave,” with the aim of spreading Japan’s esteemed coffee
                style across the globe. Our vision goes beyond coffee as just a
                beverage. We aim to deliver an experience that embodies respect
                and diversity in every cup, offering a sustainable and graceful
                “experience” through beautiful coffee-making rituals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="future-coffee__purpose">
            <b class="future-coffee__purpose-title">Project Purpose</b>
            <p class="future-coffee__purpose-descr font-text-content">
              The 4th Wave Project seeks to revive Japan’s traditional nel drip
              brewing method and share its elegant extraction process with the
              world. By doing so, we aim to make the act of brewing coffee a
              mindful experience, allowing users to savor the rich flavors and
              aromas in a deeply personal way. We are also committed to
              developing eco-friendly products that reduce environmental impact,
              aligning with our sustainability goals.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="future-coffee__features">
            <div class="future-coffee__features-item">
              <div class="future-coffee__features-item-media">
                <Image src={FutureCoffeeFeatureImg1} alt="Global Expansion" />
              </div>
              <div class="future-coffee__features-item-descr">
                <b class="future-coffee__features-item-descr-title"
                  >Global <br />
                  Expansion</b
                >
                <p
                  class="future-coffee__features-item-descr-text font-text-content"
                >
                  In February 2026, KOPPE plans to open its flagship store in
                  the United States. This store will be a space where innovation
                  meets tradition, offering an immersive experience that
                  introduces a new coffee culture to coffee lovers worldwide.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="future-coffee__features-item">
              <div class="future-coffee__features-item-media">
                <Image
                  src={FutureCoffeeFeatureImg2}
                  alt="Toward a Sustainable Future"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="future-coffee__features-item-descr">
                <b class="future-coffee__features-item-descr-title"
                  >Toward a Sustainable Future</b
                >
                <p
                  class="future-coffee__features-item-descr-text font-text-content"
                >
                  KOPPE is actively addressing the “2050 Problem” that the
                  coffee industry faces, promoting environmental conservation
                  and ethical production practices. With respect for all
                  stakeholders, we are working towards building a sustainable
                  coffee culture that looks to the future.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="future-coffee__features-item">
