                  KOPPE aims to create a “Coffee Community DAO” (Decentralized
                  Autonomous Organization), where users can connect, share
                  diverse brewing methods, and styles. This DAO will serve as a
                  platform for coffee enthusiasts to collaborate, learn from one
                  another, and develop the coffee culture together. The
                  community members will take the lead in creating new coffee
                  experiences and growing together.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
