                >“Exodus from <br /> the Land of Hope” <br /> Film Adaptation Project</b
              >
              <p class="future-film__feature-item-descr font-text-content">
                Adapting Ryu Murakami’s Masterpiece “Exodus from the Land of
                Hope” into Film This project aims to adapt Ryu Murakami’s
                globally renowned novel Exodus from the Land of Hope into a
                film. The story portrays a society that has lost hope, where a
                group of middle school students independently create their own
                economy and carve out a future for themselves. Having secured
                the copyright for this work, we are now adapting it for a modern
                audience, delivering it to viewers around the world with an
                updated approach.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="future-film__feature-item">
              <b class="future-film__feature-item-title"
                >Depicting <br />the Future of DAOs through Film</b
              >
              <p class="future-film__feature-item-descr font-text-content">
                The organization formed by the middle school students in Exodus
                from the Land of Hope closely resembles what we now know as a
                DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organization), which is currently
                gaining attention. Through this film adaptation, we aim to help
                viewers naturally understand the concept of DAOs. By
                illustrating the DAO structure in an easy-to-understand way
                through the storyline, we hope to communicate the vast potential
                of this new economic system.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="future-film__feature-item">
              <b class="future-film__feature-item-title"
                >Expanding into <br />the Real World</b
              >
              <p class="future-film__feature-item-descr font-text-content">
                The ultimate goal of this project is to recreate the DAO and the
                economic system, including the fictional currency “EXO,”
                depicted in the film, in the real world. By integrating the
                media and economic systems shown in the film with real-world
                Web3.0 technology, we plan to build a platform that anyone can
                participate in. This will link the fictional world of the film
                with reality, allowing viewers to experience a new culture that
                bridges both worlds.
              </p>
            </div>
